data-anchor=\"carrelage\">\n    <div class=\"title reveal\">\n        <h2><a href=\"carrelage\">Carrelage</a></h2>\n    </div>\n    <div class=\"wrapper carrelage\">\n        <div class=\"background\">\n            <img src=\"skins/desktop/images/home/carrelage-bg.jpg\" class=\"bg\" alt=\"fond carrelage\">\n            <img <div class=\"text\">\n            <span>Bienvenue sur le plus grand choix de carrelage</span>\n            <p>Découvrez-ici le plus grand choix de carreaux de France pour donner vie à toutes vos envies. Bénéficiez d'un large choix de carrelage de grandes marques pour aménager votre intérieur ou extérieur. Au sol ou aux murs, les qualités du <strong>carrelage</strong> permettent à ce revêtement de s'adapter à toutes les situations. Il ne vous reste plus qu’à choisir !</p>\n            <a href=\"carrelage\" class=\"btn\"><span>CHOISIR MON CARRELAGE</span></a>\n            <ul>\n                                    <li><a href=\"carrelage/sol\">Carrelage sol</a></li>\n                                    <li><a href=\"carrelage/mural-faience\">Carrelage faience</a></li>\n                                    <li><a if(tick==extent[1]){v=this.clearMaxValue;}else{v=tick;}\nticks.push({label:tick,value:this.getValue(v)});tick+=step;}\nreturn ticks;}};jvm.ColorScale=function(colors,normalizeFunction,minValue,maxValue){jvm.ColorScale.parentClass.apply(this,arguments);}\njvm.inherits(jvm.ColorScale,jvm.NumericScale);jvm.ColorScale.prototype.setScale=function(scale){var i;for(i=0;i<scale.length;i++){this.scale[i]=jvm.ColorScale.rgbToArray(scale[i]);}};jvm.ColorScale.prototype.getValue=function(value){return rgb='#',d,i;for(i=0;i<ar.length;i++){d=ar[i].toString(16);rgb+=d.length==1?'0'+d:d;}\nreturn rgb;};jvm.ColorScale.numToRgb=function(num){num=num.toString(16);while(num.length<6){num='0'+num;}\nreturn'#'+num;};jvm.ColorScale.rgbToArray=function(rgb){rgb=rgb.substr(1);return[parseInt(rgb.substr(0,2),16),parseInt(rgb.substr(2,2),16),parseInt(rgb.substr(4,2),16)];};jvm.Legend=function(params){this.params=params||{};this.map=this.params.map;this.series=this.params.series;this.body=jvm.$('<div/>');this.body.addClass('jvectormap-legend');if(this.params.cssClass){this.body.addClass(this.params.cssClass);}\nif(params.vertical){this.map.legendCntVertical.append(this.body);}else{this.map.legendCntHorizontal.append(this.body);}\nthis.render();}\njvm.Legend.prototype.render=function(){var n;}},mill:function(lat,lng,c){return{x:this.radius*(lng-c)*this.radDeg,y:-this.radius*Math.log(Math.tan((45+0.4*lat)*this.radDeg))/0.8};},mill_inv:function(x,y,c){return{lat:(2.5*Math.atan(Math.exp(0.8*y/this.radius))-5*Math.PI/8)*this.degRad,lng:(c*this.radDeg+x/this.radius)*this.degRad};},merc:function(lat,lng,c){return{x:this.radius*(lng-c)*this.radDeg,y:-this.radius*Math.log(Math.tan(Math.PI/4+lat*Math.PI/360))};},merc_inv:function(x,y,c){return{lat:(2*Math.atan(Math.exp(y/this.radius))-Math.PI/2)*this.degRad,lng:(c*this.radDeg+x/this.radius)*this.degRad};},aea:function(lat,lng,c){var fi0=0,lambda0=c*this.radDeg,fi1=29.5*this.radDeg,fi2=45.5*this.radDeg,fi=lat*this.radDeg,lambda=lng*this.radDeg,n=(Math.sin(fi1)+Math.sin(fi2))/2,C=Math.cos(fi1)*Math.cos(fi1)+2*n*Math.sin(fi1),theta=n*(lambda-lambda0),ro=Math.sqrt(C-2*n*Math.sin(fi))/n,ro0=Math.sqrt(C-2*n*Math.sin(fi0))/n;return{x:ro*Math.sin(theta)*this.radius,y:-(ro0-ro*Math.cos(theta))*this.radius};},aea_inv:function(xCoord,yCoord,c){var
